claim.claim-text:
15. A portable electronic device comprising: 
a heat source; 
at least one thermal transfer device thermally coupled to said heat source; 
at least one heat exchanger thermally coupled to each respective at least one thermal transfer device, said at least one thermal transfer device transferring heat dissipated by said heat source to said at least one heat exchanger; and 
at least one external fan disposed adjacent each respective at least one heat exchanger and thermally coupled thereto, said at least one external fan generating a flow of air to remove dissipated heat transferred from said heat source to said at least one heat exchanger.

29. A portable electronic device comprising: 
a heat source; 
a first thermal transfer device and a second thermal transfer device, each device being thermally coupled to said heat source; 
a first heat exchanger thermally coupled to said first thermal transfer device and a second heat exchanger thermally coupled to said second thermal transfer device, each of said thermal transfer devices transferring heat dissipated by said heat source to its respective heat exchanger; 
an internal fan disposed adjacent said first heat exchanger and thermally coupled thereto, said internal fan generating a flow of air to remove dissipated heat transferred from said heat source to said first heat exchanger; and 
an external fan disposed adjacent said second heat exchanger and thermally coupled thereto, said external fan generating a flow of air to remove dissipated heat transferred from said heat source to said second heat exchanger.
